high_descs: heat and remove egg from microwave
anns.task_desc: put heated egg on kitchen table

high_descs: Move to the sink on your left.
Pick up the egg in the sink.
Turn around, bring the egg to the microwave on the right.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Take the heated egg to the round table behind you.
Put the egg on the round table, right of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated egg on the round table.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink
Grab the egg out of the sink
Turn around and go to the microwave
Heat the egg in the microwave and then take it out
Turn around and go to the round table
Put the egg on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a hot egg on the round table
